Hughes added: ‘It looks likely Stephen is unavailable for two to three weeks.

‘Most people now have seen the picture and he’s had internal stitches as well as external, so it takes a little bit longer than a straightforward gash.

‘I’m disappointed as he was doing really well, filling the gap for Bojan.’ 

 

